Limmerick for Mew
Monster Rancher Metropolis: Library: Fan Fiction, Poetry, Birthday List, Links & Non-Fiction Archive: Poetry: Limmerick for Mew
By Tigerbubble on Saturday, March 2, 2002 - 01:12 pm:

Mewsneak thinks shes all flashy.
Most think she simply looks trashy.
Dressed in black leather.
Her street name is Heather.
Parts of her are quite rashy.

(Because of wearing leather all the time, keep you mind out of the gutter if you are thinking otherwise.)

This ones a little more racey than my other limerricks. I hope it isn't too over the top.
